Author: fishonthesun
Text: Maybe you could find one of those single slices of cheesecake and challenge yourself to eat it tomorrow (if fitting it into your calories would help you be less scared). If you do that, try to eat it without distractions like tv or music. Pour a nice drink (0 cal if you have to) and take a sip every bite or two. Take small bites and let it sit in your mouth to get the flavors. Even if you don't eat the whole slice, give your ED a subtle "fuck you" and enjoy something you've been craving

Author: radicalcantaloop
Text: I’ve wanted cheesecake for so long now. I could literally go out and buy one because I’m a goddamn adult. But I “can’t” because cALoRiEs. ED brain is so dumb and I hate her
